{"id": 2613, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于“维持长期友谊”，你都有哪些经验？", "description": "虽说“真正的友谊不需要刻意维护”，但既然能一直当朋友，总归是要做点什么的。（题图来自：iStock ©️ cienpies）", "record_count": 3896, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181105170326R4pSOoieamkCdGPf.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-14T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 310785, "content": "分享彼此的生活/每年能见面就见面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488912}, {"id": 310786, "content": "约饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260098}, {"id": 310787, "content": "平时多交流吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502798}, {"id": 312835, "content": "多联系，多出来聚一聚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512099}, {"id": 310788, "content": "无事分头打钱，有事随时tp。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496132}, {"id": 312068, "content": "我想要维护的时候，可能对方并不配合。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345390}, {"id": 312324, "content": "真的友谊不用刻意维持", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510418}, {"id": 310789, "content": "维护是任何关系都需要的，只是不用刻意维护而已。想到李荣浩的“有些废话还是要和你讲，讲完自己扛”", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1452830}, {"id": 313605, "content": "常联系 互相包容", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1517156}, {"id": 310790, "content": "相信對方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327700}, {"id": 318216, "content": "舒服的相处就好了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 310793, "content": "年龄越大越难交到朋友，采用必要措施维持关系，是每个人的必备功课吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1203919}, {"id": 310794, "content": "Keep 住联系", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501023}, {"id": 311562, "content": "不要跟a朋友吐槽b朋友，不管a和b认不认识", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505873}, {"id": 310795, "content": "只要你需要我 我就愿意陪你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293596}, {"id": 311563, "content": "异地的断断续续打个电话唠嗑\n同城的断断续续出来见面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423751}, {"id": 314123, "content": "信任", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821543}, {"id": 310797, "content": "在惺惺相惜里保持着和而不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501293}, {"id": 311565, "content": "不要麻烦对方 对方有需要的时候尽力去帮忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505890}, {"id": 310799, "content": "不要太黏糊 \n任何关系都需要一定神秘感\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502858}, {"id": 310801, "content": "抽时间痛饮一下。", "image": "img/option/option/20181114191135S0sFKWlJa9jx7Vz3.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838601}, {"id": 311569, "content": "留有自己的空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505907}, {"id": 310802, "content": "保持一份长期的、真正的友谊，我觉得最重要的是不断提高自己。只有自己是一个有价值的朋友，彼此的友谊才会更加的健康牢固。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502867}, {"id": 310803, "content": "别骗自己了。没有什么能长青的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43635}, {"id": 310804, "content": "一起睡一次", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200891}, {"id": 311316, "content": "我正烦恼要怎么保持友谊地久天长呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1504579}, {"id": 310805, "content": "不联系", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779398}, {"id": 311573, "content": "每年还是见一两次吧或者线上联系一两次", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1388056}, {"id": 310806, "content": "互相倾听", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797191}, {"id": 311062, "content": "你需要的时候，我都在啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1503790}, {"id": 310807, "content": "不要质疑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502895}, {"id": 310809, "content": "有事要说 不要有不好的眼神脸色", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502904}, {"id": 310811, "content": "真正的友谊不用维持", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1495913}, {"id": 310812, "content": "对理解的人，开放式的表达", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699564}, {"id": 310813, "content": "不需要刻意，就这样每天说话都不厌倦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390820}, {"id": 310814, "content": "主动一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502919}, {"id": 310815, "content": "不要以自我为中心，想着能为朋友做什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488160}, {"id": 310816, "content": "时不时聊一下彼此的日常，虽然大多数是在倒苦水", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181750}, {"id": 310818, "content": "最坚固的友谊不需要维持，就算很久不联系情谊也依然不会因为时间而减少", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502929}, {"id": 310819, "content": "距离产生美", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483068}, {"id": 310820, "content": "别强求", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496140}, {"id": 311844, "content": "想得到怎样的关系就先要怎样关心盆友\n恋人同理", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508007}, {"id": 310821, "content": "搓一顿，不行就两顿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332148}, {"id": 310822, "content": "多吃饭多说话多看电影多去浪...多发红包", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302647}, {"id": 310823, "content": "定期送对方一些小礼物 给彼此一些惊喜", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1502981}, {"id": 311591, "content": "保持一定距离 不要天天黏在一起", "image": "img/option/option/20181117214307t5NnEp3JzKfbhOXj", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686950}, {"id": 310824, "content": "距离产生美，真的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469101}, {"id": 311080, "content": "尽量多碰面，关心她/他遇到的问题和成长，记得对她/他重要的事情或日子，了解到每个人都有关注的点和在意的重心，然后保持尊重的距离", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774494}, {"id": 310825, "content": "一起打游戏，这是比较便捷又有趣又不怕尴尬的维持手段了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174794}, {"id": 311081, "content": "无话不谈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1503832}]}